-- China Will Simplify Foreign Investment Approvals, Commerce Ministry Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-03-07T01:28:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-07/china-will-simplify-foreign-investment-approvals-commerce-ministry-says.html
China will further simplify the
procedure for approvals of foreign investment in the country,
the Ministry of Commerce said today in a statement before a
briefing in Beijing.  China will also boost imports of energy, raw materials,
advanced equipment and consumer products, the ministry said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Scott Lanman at 
 slanman@bloomberg.net  